  "detailed_description": "<strong>The world is in danger, but no worries, you are here to save the day!<br>Destroy the asteroids!<br>Pew pew pew, KaBOOM! </strong><br><br>KaBoom! is an arcade game which includes an easy to start but hard to master mechanic, where you can destroy asteroids by firing the correct laser!<br>And there will be plenty of power ups to aid you in your journey!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055370/extras/1598b805ec32a50a62fb576a5f7f9762.poster.avif?t=1661363402\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055370/extras/1598b805ec32a50a62fb576a5f7f9762.webm?t=1661363402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055370/extras/1598b805ec32a50a62fb576a5f7f9762.mp4?t=1661363402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The higher your score, the harder the game becomes! Reach new highscores to unlock new gorgeous skins for your spaceship!<br>All while enjoying the <i>ear meltingly</i> good chiptune OST!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055370/extras/a0cb3805e8fb0d019598d479a571c609.poster.avif?t=1661363402\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055370/extras/a0cb3805e8fb0d019598d479a571c609.webm?t=1661363402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055370/extras/a0cb3805e8fb0d019598d479a571c609.mp4?t=1661363402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
